<div class="content-h1"><h1>ISO FIX儿童座椅接口</h1></div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="place">
<p id="openCatp" style="display:none">开放分类：<a href="//fenlei.baike.com/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E7%94%A8%E5%93%81/?prd=zhengwenye_left_kaifangfenlei" target="_blank" title="生活用品">生活用品</a></p>
</div>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="information" id="unifyprompt"><div class="summary" id="anchor" name="anchor">
		请用一段简单的话描述该词条，马上<a action="editsummaryhref" href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="editSummary();return false;">添加摘要</a>。
		</div></div>
<input id="doctitle" name="doctitle" type="hidden" value="ISO FIX儿童座椅接口"/><div id="hd_ad_doc_109"> </div>
<div class="imper-rm">本词条内容尚未完善，欢迎各位<a href="/editdocauth/ISO+FIX%E5%84%BF%E7%AB%A5%E5%BA%A7%E6%A4%85%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3" onclick="return editdoc();">编辑词条</a>，贡献自己的专业知识！</div>
<div id="float_section" style="display:none;">
<div class="catalog">
<div class="full-list">
